Puppet module: rsyslog

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages rsyslog software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include rsyslog              # Install and run rsyslog with standard configurations.
include rsyslog::disable     # Disable rsyslog service.
include rsyslog::disableboot # Disable rsyslog service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include rsyslog::absent      # Remove rsyslog package.

DEPENDENCIES:
